<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>When i use the Zend_Config with string that contains quotes, it returns a wrong value with the escape chars.
Ex:
some.ini</p>

<p>[production]
text = "<b><font>SOMETHING</font></b>"</p>

<p>Using Zend_Config:
$config = new Zend_Config_Ini('/path/to/ini/some.ini', 'production');
echo $config-&gt;text;</p>

<p>Expected:
<b><font color="#FF0000">SOMETHING</font></b></p>

<p>Returned:
<b><font>SOMETHING</font></b></p>

